room_title: Escape room "Houdini's Challenge" by Paradox Challenge Rooms in Tupelo
room_description: You won a private dinner with Houdini, but when you show up to his house, you find yourself in the middle of a battle between Houdini and an upcoming magician intent on stealing Houdini’s book of secrets. Will you be able to solve the puzzles in Houdini’s house to save his magic and your life, or will you perish with his secrets?
